        "message": "=<div style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#f4f7fb;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#1f2937;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);border:1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n      <div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb,#7c3aed);padding:28px 32px;color:#ffffff;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;opacity:0.9;\">ContentPilot Approval</div>\n        <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 0;font-size:26px;line-height:1.25;font-weight:700;\">Нова статия за преглед</h1>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"padding:32px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin:0 0 18px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;\">Здравейте,</p>\n\n        <p style=\"margin:0 0 24px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;\">\n          Моля, прегледайте статията и изберете дали е готова за публикуване.\n        </p>\n\n        <div style=\"background:#f9fafb;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:0 0 28px;\">\n          <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:8px;\">\n            Статия\n          </div>\n\n          <h2 style=\"font-size:20px;margin:0 0 14px;color:#111827;line-height:1.35;\">\n            {{ $json.article_title }}\n          </h2>\n\n          <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#374151;white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0 0 18px;\">\n            {{ $json.content }}\n          </p>\n\n          <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;\">\n            <a href=\"{{ $json.doc_link }}\" style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.5;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;\">\n              Отвори Google Doc →\n            </a>\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div style=\"text-align:center;margin:32px 0;\">\n<a href=\"{{ $json.approval_resume_url }}{{ $json.approval_resume_url.includes('?') ? '&' : '?' }}decision=approve&article_title={{ encodeURIComponent($json.article_title) }}&doc_link={{ encodeURIComponent($json.doc_link) }}&platform={{ encodeURIComponent($json.platform || 'wordpress') }}\">\n  ✅ Одобрявам\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"{{ $json.approval_resume_url }}{{ $json.approval_resume_url.includes('?') ? '&' : '?' }}decision=reject&article_title={{ encodeURIComponent($json.article_title) }}&doc_link={{ encodeURIComponent($json.doc_link) }}&platform={{ encodeURIComponent($json.platform || 'wordpress') }}\">\n  ❌ Отхвърлям\n</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding-top:18px;margin-top:28px;\">\n          <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;line-height:1.5;\">\n            След клик parent workflow-ът ще продължи автоматично в n8n чрез Wait node.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:18px 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af;\">\n      Автоматично съобщение от ContentPilot AI Content Factory\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</div>",
