    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "CP-04-Approval-Flow-Bonus\n\nSub-workflow that handles human approval before publishing.\n\nSteps:\n1. Receives article title, content, document link, platform, and approval resume URL.\n2. Prepares the approval data.\n3. Sends an email with Approve and Reject buttons.\n4. Waits for the user to click one of the approval buttons.\n5. Reads the approval decision from the button click.\n6. Normalizes the result as approved or rejected.\n7. Sends a confirmation email depending on the decision.\n8. Returns the approval status back to the main pipeline.",
        "height": 240,
        "width": 440
      },
